WEBVTT

00:07.031 --> 00:12.491
(Ding)

00:24.401 --> 00:27.231
You need to get proper rest.

00:27.401 --> 00:28.861
It's a head injury.

00:28.881 --> 00:30.311
It's not a trivial matter.

00:31.131 --> 00:32.381
It's only a minor injury.

00:32.611 --> 00:33.781
I've already recovered.

00:35.481 --> 00:36.890
But your old shoulder injury acts up

00:36.891 --> 00:38.421
every time it rains.

00:38.571 --> 00:39.911
It has been five years already.

00:41.161 --> 00:42.301
I'm fine.

00:42.311 --> 00:44.521
Futing gets a lot of rain
and has a high humidity level.

00:45.761 --> 00:47.511
Maybe a trip to the capital

00:48.251 --> 00:49.631
will actually do me good.

01:05.081 --> 01:06.381
Officer Chen,

01:06.721 --> 01:09.151
why did His Majesty summon

01:10.291 --> 01:12.231
Duke of Ding to the capital?

01:12.881 --> 01:14.151
I dare not guess

01:14.211 --> 01:16.311
His Majesty's intentions.

01:18.801 --> 01:19.951
Sir, please be rest assured.

01:20.011 --> 01:22.151
Duke of Ding is someone we all respect.

01:22.241 --> 01:24.151
His visit is just a routine matter.

01:24.411 --> 01:26.181
We ensure Duke of Ding's safety.

01:26.601 --> 01:27.741
Yuantang,

01:27.801 --> 01:28.941
stop scaring him.

01:29.161 --> 01:30.591
Don't frown all the time.

01:30.801 --> 01:31.941
It's all right.

01:32.321 --> 01:33.520
Most likely,

01:33.521 --> 01:34.960
His Majesty summons me back

01:34.961 --> 01:36.541
to report on the maritime disaster.

01:36.721 --> 01:37.861
Remember

01:38.051 --> 01:39.661
to take care of my wife.

01:43.411 --> 01:44.551
Let's go, Duke of Ding.

02:01.441 --> 02:03.690
Marshal, though the hurricane
and tsunami have passed,

02:03.691 --> 02:06.160
over a hundred household
still haven't repaired their homes.

02:06.161 --> 02:07.601
How do we handle the relief efforts?

02:08.601 --> 02:10.941
Soldiers of the Ding Army,
heed my orders!

02:12.091 --> 02:13.831
Even if the sky has fallen,

02:14.091 --> 02:15.591
do not stop the relief efforts!

02:15.761 --> 02:17.271
Once the drainage is done,

02:18.041 --> 02:19.850
we need to help
the people plant their crops.

02:19.851 --> 02:21.461
Only when the seedlings are planted

02:21.971 --> 02:23.551
will the people's hearts be at ease.

02:23.921 --> 02:25.250
Do you understand?

02:25.251 --> 02:26.391
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

02:32.571 --> 02:33.711
Marshal!

02:54.761 --> 02:55.850
The Duke of Ding's Resident

02:55.851 --> 02:57.570
is surrounded by the Shadow Guard.

02:57.571 --> 02:58.831
No one can get in or out.

03:00.371 --> 03:01.551
How could this happen?

03:05.601 --> 03:08.551
I'm afraid this case
isn't as simple as it seems.

03:11.851 --> 03:12.991
Sir,

03:13.091 --> 03:14.970
(Duke of Ding's Residence)
the front and back are guarded,

03:14.971 --> 03:16.591
with about forty or fifty men in total.

03:17.481 --> 03:19.551
If the emperor only wanted
a simple audience,

03:19.571 --> 03:21.391
why would he go to such lengths?

03:22.371 --> 03:23.400
Sir,

03:23.401 --> 03:24.250
let's charge in

03:24.251 --> 03:25.850
and rescue Duke of Ding's family.

03:25.851 --> 03:26.991
Yes.

03:28.131 --> 03:29.551
Don't act rashly.

03:31.761 --> 03:32.850
Wait here for me.

03:32.851 --> 03:33.991
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

05:26.391 --> 05:28.730
=Blossom=

05:28.731 --> 05:30.590
(Adapted from the novel
"Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

05:30.591 --> 05:33.851
=Episode 5=

05:34.831 --> 05:38.371
(Half a Month Later)

05:48.021 --> 05:49.581
I apologize for disturbing you so late.

05:49.761 --> 05:52.261
My master's surname is Mei
and a merchant from the south.

05:52.341 --> 05:55.071
We're passing through this area
and need a place to stay for the night.

06:09.131 --> 06:10.271
Young Lady, you're up.

06:11.131 --> 06:12.431
What's the hour now?

06:12.751 --> 06:14.501
Just past three-quarters
after the Yin hour.

06:17.371 --> 06:18.511
Young Lady,

06:19.011 --> 06:21.311
a group of merchants arrived
at the manor.

06:21.401 --> 06:23.231
The head calls himself, Mr. Mei.

06:23.441 --> 06:25.930
But I noticed everyone
in the group walks quietly,

06:25.931 --> 06:27.381
with calloused palms.

06:27.571 --> 06:29.400
Mr. Chen has sent people here
multiple times,

06:29.401 --> 06:30.871
to ask if you've woken up.

06:32.961 --> 06:34.501
Bring Mr. Chen here.

06:37.131 --> 06:39.911
The servants inside the manor
are very tight-lipped.

06:40.321 --> 06:42.941
All we know is that the one in charge
is called Fourth Young Lady.

06:43.961 --> 06:45.111
Fourth Young Lady?

06:45.251 --> 06:48.920
We're probably in trouble now.

06:48.921 --> 06:51.170
Those visitors are no ordinary people.

06:51.171 --> 06:53.671
They're from Duke of Ding's forces.

06:53.931 --> 06:55.381
How can you tell?

06:55.611 --> 06:58.381
The scholar in green
who calls himself the accountant,

06:58.611 --> 07:01.311
is Yan Chaoqing.

07:01.321 --> 07:02.690
He's one of Duke of Ding's

07:02.691 --> 07:04.741
most trusted subordinates.

07:07.251 --> 07:08.741
Do you know him?

07:09.811 --> 07:11.471
I'm grateful for your kind attention.

07:11.961 --> 07:13.471
I've kept

07:15.051 --> 07:16.471
some of my past hidden.

07:16.641 --> 07:17.821
But I won't mistake him.

07:18.051 --> 07:20.960
He used to be an advisor to Zhang Kai,
Futing's former Grand Coordinator.

07:20.961 --> 07:23.570
I know his real name isn't Chen Qushui,

07:23.571 --> 07:24.791
but Chen Bo.

07:24.961 --> 07:28.431
The one my uncle executed
on the battlefield?

07:30.251 --> 07:31.671
Fifteen years ago,

07:31.691 --> 07:34.181
Dongyu pirates besieged Futing.

07:34.281 --> 07:36.400
- Official Zhang Kai abandoned the city
- Stop right there!

07:36.401 --> 07:39.471
but was captured and executed
by Duke of Ding.

07:39.641 --> 07:40.991
My former superior

07:41.761 --> 07:43.381
was Zhang Kai.

07:47.511 --> 07:48.880
The shame of abandoning the city.

07:48.881 --> 07:51.010
Yan Chaoqing would definitely see me

07:51.011 --> 07:52.621
as a dishonorable person.

07:53.131 --> 07:54.581
I've caused you trouble.

07:54.841 --> 07:55.981
I...

08:02.761 --> 08:03.750
Please get up, Mr. Chen.

08:03.751 --> 08:06.370
(Graceful and Refined)

08:06.371 --> 08:09.351
When I appointed you as my advisor,

08:09.351 --> 08:10.821
I promised not to ask about your past.

08:11.281 --> 08:12.901
Your former superior
was afraid of death.

08:13.011 --> 08:14.551
It wasn't something you could stop.

08:16.281 --> 08:17.821
What I'm worried about

08:18.491 --> 08:20.701
is that Zhending has no food to give out

08:21.171 --> 08:22.381
or troops to lend out.

08:22.611 --> 08:25.031
Why are they here
with their identities hidden?

08:25.961 --> 08:28.141
That Mr. Mei is carrying a baby.

08:28.571 --> 08:29.711
A baby?

08:33.521 --> 08:36.391
(The lonely subject glances
at the cold sea waves.)

08:36.521 --> 08:39.181
(Ten years guarding the southeast
with a cold heart.)

08:39.251 --> 08:42.081
(Only regret being caught in a rainstorm
during a long and endless night.)

08:42.281 --> 08:44.074
(Duke of Radiant Sea)
(Where can the crying orphan)

08:44.075 --> 08:45.911
(Duke of Radiant Sea)
(find refuge?)

08:47.081 --> 08:49.201
Caught in a rainstorm
during a long and endless night.

08:50.281 --> 08:52.061
Where can the orphan find refuge?

08:54.531 --> 08:56.210
Something bad has happened to Duke of Ding.

08:58.521 --> 08:59.661
Madam.

09:07.311 --> 09:09.181
does the baby still spit out
the milk before sleeping?

09:10.091 --> 09:11.631
He's much better after being indoors.

09:12.041 --> 09:14.400
It's just that we've been traveling
for several days,

09:14.401 --> 09:16.130
and with the heavy rain and rough roads.

09:16.131 --> 09:17.791
If we didn't stop to rest,

09:18.521 --> 09:20.461
I was afraid the baby wouldn't hold up.

09:22.401 --> 09:24.861
Don't worry, we're almost there.

09:27.561 --> 09:29.551
The mind of a monarch
is hard to understand.

09:30.281 --> 09:32.461
Your uncle's fate is uncertain.

09:33.281 --> 09:34.821
Under these circumstances,

09:35.281 --> 09:37.431
it looks like the whole family
won't be able to escape.

09:37.671 --> 09:39.130
(Madam Liu, Duchess of Ding)

09:39.131 --> 09:42.311
He's your uncle's only bloodline.

09:42.731 --> 09:45.400
Aunt, I'll take both of you away with me.

09:45.401 --> 09:46.701
No one can leave

09:47.491 --> 09:49.151
under this circumstance.

09:49.521 --> 09:50.911
You knew that.

09:52.611 --> 09:54.151
Protect him for me.

09:55.851 --> 09:56.991
Aunt,

09:57.091 --> 09:58.391
I swear on my life

09:58.851 --> 10:03.061
that he won't shed
a single drop of blood.

10:07.401 --> 10:09.370
The Duke is deeply favored
by the emperor.

10:09.371 --> 10:12.400
He also won a great victory
at the Boat Island earlier this year.

10:12.401 --> 10:14.280
When Futing was hit by the hurricane,

10:14.281 --> 10:16.010
he personally led the troops to aid
in disaster relief.

10:16.011 --> 10:17.751
The scribes at the capital

10:17.851 --> 10:19.730
didn't even hear anything about this.

10:19.731 --> 10:21.551
Duke of Ding is a duke of the highest rank,

10:22.621 --> 10:24.731
with Ding Army of fifty thousand men
under his command.

10:24.731 --> 10:26.370
If something really happens,
a secret order will be issued

10:26.371 --> 10:27.861
to let the Shadow Guards take charge.

10:28.561 --> 10:30.330
Otherwise,
it will stir up a military uprising.

10:30.331 --> 10:32.010
How will the imperial court deal
with that, then?

10:32.011 --> 10:34.101
How do you know about this?

10:36.681 --> 10:37.911
It has always been like this

10:37.921 --> 10:39.491
when a ruler is threatened
by a great person.

10:39.491 --> 10:41.031
Speaking of the baby,

10:42.321 --> 10:44.640
in the Ninth month of last year,
we received a letter from Futing

10:44.641 --> 10:46.031
mentioning

10:46.561 --> 10:49.271
that Duke of Ding's Residence
was purchasing baby supplies.

10:50.251 --> 10:53.061
The one expecting must be the Duchess.

10:57.281 --> 10:59.791
If the family is really
on the brink of collapse,

10:59.971 --> 11:01.551
it is hard to entrust the orphan.

11:02.761 --> 11:05.031
I make things even worse in an instant.

11:05.281 --> 11:09.701
They won't leave any loose ends.

11:10.761 --> 11:13.701
So, you know Mr. Mei?

11:16.161 --> 11:18.861
Mr. Mei may be young.

11:18.911 --> 11:20.821
But he carries himself
with an imposing presence.

11:21.161 --> 11:24.751
The others treat him
with exceptional respect.

11:25.971 --> 11:27.181
A young person like him

11:28.091 --> 11:31.941
is able to mobilize Duke of Ding's
elite forces at a time like this.

11:34.041 --> 11:35.271
In this situation,

11:37.161 --> 11:38.581
only Song Mo can do it.

11:38.801 --> 11:39.941
Song Mo?

11:40.131 --> 11:42.640
The one who led a surprise attack
on Yu Island at just thirteen

11:42.641 --> 11:44.431
and secured a great victory
at Boat Island

11:44.491 --> 11:46.391
earlier this year amidst a crisis.

11:46.681 --> 11:48.151
If it's really him,

11:48.801 --> 11:51.821
we have no chance of escaping.

11:53.131 --> 11:54.271
I've scouted around.

11:54.851 --> 11:56.061
There are forty-two women,

11:56.131 --> 11:57.631
twenty servants and attendants,

11:58.091 --> 12:01.040
and one elderly woman
being cared for by a maid.

12:01.041 --> 12:02.181
She has gone to bed.

12:02.451 --> 12:04.791
Lu Zheng and Lu Ming
are guarding the exits.

12:05.041 --> 12:06.701
Everything is in place.

12:10.131 --> 12:11.090
Fourth Young Lady,

12:11.091 --> 12:13.551
about ten people
from the merchant convoy are missing.

12:14.611 --> 12:16.311
They have surrounded the manor's exits

12:16.801 --> 12:18.341
and planned to wipe us out.

12:21.491 --> 12:22.631
Let it be.

12:22.801 --> 12:24.760
It all started because of me

12:24.761 --> 12:26.431
so I'll take responsibility for this.

12:26.561 --> 12:27.941
I'll go and find them

12:28.131 --> 12:30.061
and let them kill only me.

12:30.851 --> 12:31.991
Mr. Chen,

12:33.441 --> 12:36.431
hiding a noble orphan is punishable
by the extermination of the entire clan.

12:36.611 --> 12:37.751
If it were me,

12:38.161 --> 12:39.301
for the child,

12:39.561 --> 12:40.701
for my subordinates,

12:40.851 --> 12:41.991
and for my family,

12:42.041 --> 12:43.791
I would eliminate everyone who knew too.

12:46.611 --> 12:47.911
To avoid drawing attention,

12:48.161 --> 12:50.391
they'll make their move
before dawn and the rain stops.

12:51.011 --> 12:52.551
We don't have much time left.

12:53.221 --> 12:55.381
Go and tell Ms. Tuo
to secure all the doors and windows.

12:55.801 --> 12:57.151
Don't alarm Grandmother.

12:57.351 --> 13:01.171
(Bide Time, Gather Strength)

13:02.191 --> 13:03.331
Hush.

13:05.011 --> 13:06.010
Your Lordship,

13:06.011 --> 13:07.160
they're making a move.

13:07.161 --> 13:08.431
Do you want us to...

13:12.491 --> 13:15.151
I know you never harm women or children.

13:15.401 --> 13:18.551
But to protect the Young Lord,
there's no other choice.

13:19.881 --> 13:22.101
That Chen is vile and dishonorable.

13:22.371 --> 13:24.911
I'm sure those with him are the same.

13:26.161 --> 13:27.581
If this matter gets out,

13:28.651 --> 13:30.311
the consequences will be unimaginable.

13:33.451 --> 13:35.061
Uncle only has this one son.

13:35.521 --> 13:38.391
I've sworn to Aunt
that I'd keep him safe.

13:40.161 --> 13:43.181
If heaven punishes me
or I end up in hell for this,

13:44.371 --> 13:45.511
so be it.

13:47.401 --> 13:48.631
Make it quick and quiet.

13:49.211 --> 13:50.431
Don't wake the children.

13:50.451 --> 13:51.591
Yes, sir.

14:15.300 --> 14:16.421
Fourth Young Lady,

14:16.711 --> 14:18.311
you're heading out on this rainy night.

14:18.731 --> 14:20.181
Where are you going in such a hurry?

14:21.131 --> 14:22.431
It's such a stormy weather.

14:23.131 --> 14:25.861
I can escort you all the way.

14:36.161 --> 14:37.301
Fighting them is futile.

14:38.011 --> 14:39.221
No one within a hundred steps

14:39.681 --> 14:41.791
can escape from the military crossbows.

14:42.491 --> 14:43.631
Forgive me.

14:50.971 --> 14:52.181
Your Lordship, this move

14:53.251 --> 14:54.551
is a serious mistake.

14:58.561 --> 14:59.861
What did you call me?

15:00.251 --> 15:02.061
Duke of Ding defied the imperial order

15:02.061 --> 15:04.210
and raided homes without authorization
to provide disaster relief.

15:04.211 --> 15:06.611
He's being escorted back to the capital
under charges of treason

15:06.611 --> 15:07.941
with all his family members
being detained.

15:09.401 --> 15:11.631
You and Duke of Ding
are close like father and son.

15:12.401 --> 15:14.221
You travel with a baby
on this stormy night.

15:14.731 --> 15:17.151
Are you trying to hide away

15:18.161 --> 15:19.981
Duke of Ding's only bloodline?

15:21.491 --> 15:22.631
Who are you?

15:23.321 --> 15:25.271
I'm from the Palace Surveillance
of Palace Women.

15:25.491 --> 15:28.061
His Majesty knew
you would make this move

15:28.641 --> 15:30.280
so he sent me here

15:30.281 --> 15:31.631
to deliver his oral decree.

15:32.011 --> 15:33.911
So, do you intend

15:33.971 --> 15:35.941
to share Duke of Ding's guilt for treason?

15:49.211 --> 15:51.911
Chen Shun has always been in charge
of the Palace Surveillance.

15:53.161 --> 15:54.581
Are you one of his people?

15:56.011 --> 15:57.671
No need to test me, Your Lordship.

15:57.921 --> 15:59.431
There's no one by the name of Chen Shun

15:59.881 --> 16:01.511
within the six services and the office.

16:01.741 --> 16:03.071
Where's your official badge?

16:04.641 --> 16:05.781
(Official badge?)

16:43.881 --> 16:45.021
Song Mo.

16:45.641 --> 16:47.271
Since you knew my name,

16:47.921 --> 16:50.981
you would how many corrupt officials
and pirates I've interrogated.

16:51.281 --> 16:52.800
You could fake it to a certain extent

16:52.801 --> 16:54.671
because you know a little
about those in the palace.

16:55.371 --> 16:56.951
But when it comes to the finer details,

16:57.641 --> 16:59.271
your uneasiness gives you away.

17:11.211 --> 17:12.551
Your palm is sweaty.

17:14.121 --> 17:16.791
You couldn't have orchestrated it alone.

17:17.791 --> 17:18.981
Who are you working for?

17:20.641 --> 17:21.781
Tell me

17:22.071 --> 17:23.611
and I'll leave you a whole corpse.

17:26.271 --> 17:27.411
Young Lady!

17:27.921 --> 17:29.061
We got them!

17:43.511 --> 17:45.941
You're here to distract me to buy time.

17:46.441 --> 17:47.611
You tricked me.

17:47.841 --> 17:49.091
I meant no harm.

17:49.681 --> 17:50.920
This was the only way

17:50.921 --> 17:52.230
to get you to sit down

17:52.231 --> 17:53.701
and have a proper conversation with me.

17:53.711 --> 17:55.400
There's no need to waste words
with them, Young Lady.

17:55.401 --> 17:57.291
We have the child in our hands.

17:57.311 --> 17:58.640
We'll escort you out of here.

17:58.641 --> 17:59.840
What can they possibly do?

17:59.841 --> 18:00.981
Fine!

18:01.681 --> 18:03.851
Then wake the elderly lady up
in the main hall!

18:04.161 --> 18:05.571
You can all die together!

18:07.061 --> 18:08.881
(Eternal Passage of Time)

18:16.071 --> 18:17.160
Your Lordship, wait!

18:17.161 --> 18:18.331
Do not speak recklessly!

18:18.441 --> 18:21.421
Taking the baby hostage is a way
to make a deal to satisfy both sides.

18:21.991 --> 18:23.181
Not to flee.

18:23.361 --> 18:25.771
Whether a massacre or making a deal,

18:26.751 --> 18:28.221
it's up to you to decide.

18:29.501 --> 18:33.761
(Twilight in Spring)

18:33.921 --> 18:35.901
Duke of Ding is still being escorted

18:36.401 --> 18:37.981
with his fate remains undecided.

18:38.011 --> 18:39.920
Yet here you are,
risking exposure to the yamen,

18:39.921 --> 18:42.360
or even the Ministry of Justice
and the Court of Judicial Review,

18:42.361 --> 18:43.991
attempting to slaughter everyone here
to silence them.

18:43.991 --> 18:46.221
That can only mean the person

18:46.271 --> 18:47.981
you wish to entrust the child to
is nearby, correct?

18:54.271 --> 18:56.611
Tan's Manor is far
from the imperial court

18:56.621 --> 18:57.981
and they have a reputation
for loyalty and righteousness.

18:58.161 --> 19:00.661
It's said the Tan Family
is indebted to Duke of Ding.

19:01.361 --> 19:02.981
They would indeed be an ideal choice.

19:07.071 --> 19:08.550
This woman is calculating

19:08.551 --> 19:09.981
and full of schemes.

19:10.511 --> 19:11.400
Your Lordship,

19:11.401 --> 19:13.091
don't waste time with her.

19:13.211 --> 19:15.321
There's no need to see me
as your enemy, Your Lordship.

19:15.361 --> 19:18.011
I have always held great respect
for Duke of Ding and the Jiang Clan.

19:18.751 --> 19:20.661
I wonder what the situation is like now.

19:21.551 --> 19:22.750
I only ask

19:22.751 --> 19:24.680
because the decisive issue here

19:24.681 --> 19:26.051
isn't the child,

19:26.401 --> 19:27.981
but the Duke of Ding himself.

19:28.121 --> 19:29.941
If Duke of Ding can be freed from danger,

19:30.401 --> 19:31.981
the child will naturally be safe.

19:32.591 --> 19:35.221
Then Your Lordship won't have to resort
to such dishonorable actions.

19:36.031 --> 19:38.531
Duke of Ding's loyalty and bravery
are known to all.

19:38.681 --> 19:40.981
Those in court who can see clearly

19:41.161 --> 19:42.640
will petition on his behalf.

19:42.641 --> 19:44.611
You don't have to worry
about this, miss.

19:46.031 --> 19:47.550
I'm sure Duchess Ying

19:47.551 --> 19:49.461
is already rushing around

19:49.751 --> 19:51.981
to gather old acquaintances
to submit joint petitions,

19:52.211 --> 19:53.851
pleading for justice. Is that correct?

19:54.251 --> 19:56.981
Under normal circumstances,
this would be the proper approach.

19:57.511 --> 20:00.051
But Duke of Ding is no ordinary person.

20:00.071 --> 20:01.371
Such good intentions

20:01.921 --> 20:04.501
might only end up
as a death sentence for Duke of Ding.

20:06.231 --> 20:07.501
How dare

20:07.681 --> 20:09.221
a country girl speak such nonsense?

20:09.361 --> 20:10.501
You...

20:11.471 --> 20:12.611
Fourth Young Lady,

20:13.841 --> 20:14.981
please continue.

20:15.911 --> 20:17.920
But back in the day,
when Wang Jian asked for land,

20:17.921 --> 20:19.871
Emperor Qin Shi Huang brushed it off
with a laugh.

20:19.881 --> 20:21.221
Xiao He defamed himself,

20:21.231 --> 20:22.880
and Emperor Gaozu of Han
never doubted him.

20:22.881 --> 20:25.400
Zhou Yafu had achievements
in conquering seven kingdoms.

20:25.401 --> 20:27.221
But he died unjustly

20:27.401 --> 20:29.221
over a few slanderous words.

20:29.681 --> 20:30.821
Why?

20:32.831 --> 20:34.411
When one's success
overshadows the ruler,

20:34.411 --> 20:36.611
there will always be envious people
who will spread lies,

20:37.071 --> 20:38.901
with the intention to mislead the ruler.

20:40.471 --> 20:41.701
As Su Ziyun once said,

20:42.161 --> 20:44.701
"First, there is doubt,

20:44.751 --> 20:47.680
and then slander takes root."

20:47.681 --> 20:50.611
If His Majesty
hadn't already harbored suspicion,

20:51.071 --> 20:53.680
those lies wouldn't have succeeded.

20:53.681 --> 20:55.571
What does a traitor like you know

20:55.601 --> 20:57.221
about loyalty between ruler and subject?

20:57.271 --> 21:01.461
A mass petition will only be seen
as a challenge to imperial authority,

21:01.601 --> 21:03.270
a faction pressuring the throne.

21:03.271 --> 21:06.120
Do you think
His Majesty would feel more assured

21:06.121 --> 21:07.461
or more threatened by that?

21:11.161 --> 21:12.461
What do you think

21:13.231 --> 21:14.531
we should do?

21:15.841 --> 21:18.901
In my opinion, it would be better
to take the opposite approach.

21:19.211 --> 21:21.791
Let the officials turn against Duke of Ding
and push him further into isolation.

21:21.791 --> 21:23.421
When Duke of Ding appears to stand alone

21:23.471 --> 21:24.611
without any support,

21:24.681 --> 21:27.181
His Majesty's suspicion
will naturally ease.

21:27.841 --> 21:29.741
Out of consideration
for their friendship,

21:30.601 --> 21:33.141
the emperor would likely settle
for a small punishment.

21:33.141 --> 21:35.141
In the interest
of political stability after that,

21:35.511 --> 21:38.181
the emperor might even rely
on Duke of Ding more in the future.

21:38.961 --> 21:41.421
But who can truly understand
the emperor's thoughts?

21:41.991 --> 21:44.981
Isn't this approach too risky?

21:45.201 --> 21:47.141
You live far away
from the imperial court.

21:48.361 --> 21:50.611
But you sure know
how to read the situation

21:51.511 --> 21:53.291
and understand people's minds.

22:00.231 --> 22:03.291
How do you know so much
about Duke of Ding's case?

22:04.161 --> 22:06.221
Who exactly are you,

22:06.711 --> 22:08.571
and why are you living here in hiding?

22:34.201 --> 22:35.341
Madam!

22:43.271 --> 22:45.011
Sulan, put down your weapon.

22:45.271 --> 22:46.421
Do not act rashly.

22:47.361 --> 22:49.221
Lu Ming, tell the wet nurse to come in.

23:11.361 --> 23:12.901
The hiccup isn't stopping.

23:13.551 --> 23:15.741
Has it always been like this
since birth?

23:16.121 --> 23:17.941
Cold and sweating excessively?

23:21.161 --> 23:23.680
Suxin, warm up the goat milk
I usually prepare

23:23.681 --> 23:24.750
and bring it over.

23:24.751 --> 23:25.891
Yes.

23:26.401 --> 23:28.331
You're an unmarried young lady,

23:28.401 --> 23:30.261
and yet you know how to care for a baby?

23:30.791 --> 23:33.531
I've cared for many babies in the manor.

23:33.681 --> 23:36.091
Naturally, I know more
about this compared to men like you.

24:13.361 --> 24:15.461
He's drinking now.

24:15.931 --> 24:17.371
He was born prematurely so he's weak.

24:17.371 --> 24:18.911
He can't digest breast milk that well.

24:18.911 --> 24:20.491
So he needs to be fed with goat's milk.

24:20.711 --> 24:23.371
My manor is the only one within a hundred li
that raises goats.

24:23.681 --> 24:25.981
I'll deliver it
to Tan's Manor on time after this.

24:37.881 --> 24:39.021
Sir...

24:45.991 --> 24:47.141
Since everyone's hungry,

24:47.441 --> 24:48.771
how about putting down the weapons

24:48.921 --> 24:50.331
and we go and have a meal?

24:51.071 --> 24:52.211
That's a great idea.

25:05.401 --> 25:06.571
Move aside and let me do it.

25:06.961 --> 25:08.230
Bring several plates over here.

25:08.231 --> 25:09.371
All right.

25:15.941 --> 25:16.840
Move it here.

25:16.841 --> 25:18.421
All right, the food is here.

25:18.911 --> 25:20.251
- Nice.
- That smells delicious.

25:21.271 --> 25:22.411
They smell tasty.

25:24.361 --> 25:26.611
Come and have a meal.

25:27.551 --> 25:29.221
Please enjoy.

25:29.471 --> 25:30.510
This is delicious.

25:30.511 --> 25:32.091
Help yourselves with more food.

25:44.441 --> 25:46.771
Now, you're already involved
in this mess.

25:47.661 --> 25:49.941
If the Shadow Guards find out
that your manor is involved,

25:50.681 --> 25:53.091
do you know it's a grave crime
for failing to report this?

25:53.711 --> 25:54.851
Won't you regret it?

25:55.681 --> 25:58.051
You have people
you're willing to risk your life for.

25:58.271 --> 25:59.411
So do I.

26:00.201 --> 26:01.531
If I don't take this risk,

26:01.541 --> 26:03.471
I won't be able
to protect everyone in the manor.

26:04.311 --> 26:07.421
Besides, Duke of Ding is someone
I respect deeply.

26:10.111 --> 26:13.181
(I'm already poisoned,
and my time is running out.)

26:13.791 --> 26:16.701
(What I regret is not being able
to clear Duke of Ding's name before I die.)

26:17.531 --> 26:19.221
(Instead, I implicated you.)

26:21.161 --> 26:23.571
I don't want to see
someone being pushed onto a path

26:24.471 --> 26:26.371
they can't return from because of fate.

26:39.961 --> 26:41.421
- Let's go.
- Move it. Hurry.

26:43.031 --> 26:44.171
Sulan.

26:53.201 --> 26:54.701
Tan Manor's master is here!

26:55.341 --> 27:00.881
(Unclouded Mind)

27:01.441 --> 27:03.331
I owe my current position to the help

27:03.401 --> 27:05.011
of Duke of Ding in the past.

27:05.021 --> 27:06.431
Please rest assured, Your Lordship.

27:06.441 --> 27:09.221
I will protect his young son
with my life!

27:09.231 --> 27:10.501
Your righteousness is admirable.

27:10.961 --> 27:13.941
But today, things are different.

27:14.271 --> 27:17.840
During the flood, Fourth Young Lady helped
with disaster relief and provided food,

27:17.841 --> 27:19.091
offering kindness and aid.

27:19.271 --> 27:20.470
If it weren't for her,

27:20.471 --> 27:22.331
Tan's Manor wouldn't
have survived this crisis.

27:24.231 --> 27:26.771
I, Tan, boldly ask for a favor.

27:27.441 --> 27:29.261
We are willing
to stake our lives to vouch

27:29.311 --> 27:31.751
that Fourth Young Lady is a person
of great righteousness and honor.

27:31.751 --> 27:33.371
She would never leak
this secret to anyone!

27:33.511 --> 27:36.120
Please spare her life, Your Lordship!

27:36.121 --> 27:39.141
- Please spare her life, Your Lordship!
- Please spare her life, Your Lordship!

27:45.071 --> 27:46.211
Fourth Young Lady,

27:47.361 --> 27:48.501
your manor

27:49.641 --> 27:50.811
is safe.

27:59.861 --> 28:02.361
(Twilight in Spring)

28:02.751 --> 28:04.400
This is called dog-tail grass.

28:04.401 --> 28:06.750
See how it looks wagging back and forth

28:06.751 --> 28:08.221
like a dog's tail?

28:09.711 --> 28:10.851
Really?

28:10.961 --> 28:12.901
So this is called dog-tail grass.

28:15.121 --> 28:16.080
Oh,

28:16.081 --> 28:17.880
why are you here?

28:17.881 --> 28:19.291
Why aren't you going home?

28:19.711 --> 28:22.120
Because I have no home.

28:22.121 --> 28:23.750
Everyone has a home.

28:23.751 --> 28:25.731
Why don't you?

28:28.401 --> 28:31.221
Not everyone has a home.

28:34.881 --> 28:37.461
(He seems like
a completely different person)

28:37.841 --> 28:39.741
(from the one last night.)

28:41.751 --> 28:44.421
I've heard of your exceptional talents,
Mr. Chen.

28:44.921 --> 28:48.051
Would you consider becoming my advisor?

28:48.991 --> 28:51.181
Mr. Chen may have followed
the wrong superior back then.

28:51.401 --> 28:53.771
The decision to surrender
and abandon the city wasn't his.

28:54.121 --> 28:55.901
He's been with me
for over ten years now.

28:55.911 --> 28:57.120
He wouldn't act dishonorably.

28:57.121 --> 28:58.261
What if

28:59.121 --> 29:00.661
I insist?

29:01.991 --> 29:03.461
(Does he want to take a hostage?)

29:04.071 --> 29:05.741
(He's still wary about me.)

29:07.401 --> 29:08.901
Zhao!

29:20.121 --> 29:21.741
If you're still concerned,

29:21.961 --> 29:25.221
how about letting General Yan stay
at the manor?

29:25.271 --> 29:27.510
Once the situation calms down,
we can arrange an exchange.

29:27.641 --> 29:29.030
Wouldn't that be better for you?

29:29.031 --> 29:30.901
General Yan is one of my closest men.

29:30.921 --> 29:32.501
How could he leave my side?

29:32.921 --> 29:35.741
What if I insist too?

29:37.421 --> 29:38.920
They've prepared some snacks for you

29:38.921 --> 29:40.120
in the kitchen.

29:40.121 --> 29:41.391
- Go and have some.
- All right.

30:06.231 --> 30:07.371
Madam.

30:07.991 --> 30:09.131
Your Lordship,

30:09.351 --> 30:11.030
Young Lord just finished his goat's milk

30:11.031 --> 30:12.611
- and has fallen asleep.
- Good.

30:13.751 --> 30:16.261
Once we cross this river,
we'll reach Tan's Manor.

30:16.511 --> 30:18.661
The Young Lord will soon
be safe and sound.

30:26.831 --> 30:27.920
So, what did you find out?

30:27.921 --> 30:29.790
Your Lordship,
we manage to find out something.

30:29.791 --> 30:31.360
She's the legitimate eldest daughter
of the Dou family in the capital.

30:31.361 --> 30:32.501
Her name is Dou Zhao.

30:32.501 --> 30:34.471
Her grandmother comes
from the prestigious Cui Clan.

30:34.621 --> 30:36.640
They say she's been ruthless
and scheming since childhood

30:36.641 --> 30:37.781
for trying to seize her family's wealth.

30:37.791 --> 30:39.861
That's why her family abandoned
her here at the manor.

30:41.361 --> 30:42.501
Abandoned?

30:43.511 --> 30:45.771
Didn't my father also cast me aside
and drive me away?

30:45.791 --> 30:47.221
What good can come out

30:47.231 --> 30:48.771
of a woman's household quarrels?

30:50.031 --> 30:52.571
She's sharp, quick-witted,

30:52.711 --> 30:53.941
and highly adaptable.

30:53.971 --> 30:55.030
Her way of handling things

30:55.031 --> 30:57.011
is nothing
like the average sheltered woman.

30:57.121 --> 30:59.400
Also, the farmers in her manor

30:59.401 --> 31:00.880
are actually trained warriors.

31:00.881 --> 31:02.270
Even her two maids

31:02.271 --> 31:03.501
are skilled in martial arts.

31:04.121 --> 31:06.510
Her father works
in the Ministry of Revenue,

31:06.511 --> 31:09.270
and her uncle, Dou Shishu, was promoted
to an official in the Ministry of Rites.

31:09.271 --> 31:12.261
Last night's events weren't
as simple as they seemed.

31:14.841 --> 31:17.901
His Majesty and Duke of Ding shared
a ruler,

31:18.231 --> 31:20.571
which they split into two halves
and they each kept one.

31:21.071 --> 31:24.741
It's a symbol of trust and duty
to advise that will never change.

31:25.961 --> 31:28.701
Perhaps, the ruler's heart

31:28.911 --> 31:30.571
has always been indifferent
to his subjects.

31:31.961 --> 31:33.101
Your Lordship,

31:33.641 --> 31:35.261
when Duke of Ding returns to the capital,

31:35.751 --> 31:38.501
why not present the ruler
to His Majesty

31:38.991 --> 31:40.261
as a gesture of humility?

31:41.161 --> 31:43.571
Perhaps seeing the old relic

31:44.031 --> 31:46.701
might soften the emperor's heart
and show Duke of Ding mercy.

31:48.401 --> 31:49.771
She looked at me

31:50.961 --> 31:52.101
in a strange way,

31:52.991 --> 31:54.901
as if we had met before.

31:55.841 --> 31:57.421
I can't see through her for now.

31:58.881 --> 32:01.470
I've been away for too long
so I'm not up to date on court affairs.

32:01.471 --> 32:03.360
We need to investigate
the Dou family thoroughly,

32:03.361 --> 32:04.501
just to be safe.

32:04.921 --> 32:06.061
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

32:09.511 --> 32:10.651
Here.

32:21.791 --> 32:23.640
You were calmed
when the sword was aimed at you.

32:23.641 --> 32:25.160
Now that things have settled,

32:25.161 --> 32:26.750
why worry and fear?

32:26.751 --> 32:28.941
That calmness was just for show.

32:29.791 --> 32:32.440
I heard he's skilled
in reading facial expressions.

32:32.441 --> 32:34.901
His gaze can pierce
through someone's very bones.

32:35.231 --> 32:36.270
Now that I think about it,

32:36.271 --> 32:37.901
my heart still races with fear.

32:38.711 --> 32:41.291
I never want to see those eyes again.

32:41.881 --> 32:43.141
He's so ruthless.

32:43.231 --> 32:44.811
Why did you help him?

32:44.921 --> 32:47.221
You haven't seen him
at his most ruthless yet.

32:48.641 --> 32:50.981
If Duke of Ding really died unjustly,

32:51.121 --> 32:52.291
with his temperament,

32:52.471 --> 32:54.701
he could do even more extreme things.

32:55.201 --> 32:56.811
Then that would bring even
greater danger.

32:59.271 --> 33:00.400
By the way,

33:00.401 --> 33:02.291
did anything happen
with Grandmother last night?

33:02.471 --> 33:05.741
Before going to bed,
Old Madam burned some benzoin

33:05.741 --> 33:08.451
Since she fell into a deep sleep,
she shouldn't have noticed anything.

33:09.791 --> 33:11.661
- That's a relief.
- Zhao!

33:11.991 --> 33:13.131
Ansu?

33:17.471 --> 33:19.011
- Zhao.
- Ansu.

33:21.111 --> 33:22.790
Aren't you supposed
to go to Futing with Zhangru?

33:22.791 --> 33:24.371
Ms. Longevity! Su!

33:24.551 --> 33:25.550
Zhangru.

33:25.551 --> 33:26.920
Go to the front hall. We have good news.

33:26.921 --> 33:27.990
What good news?

33:27.991 --> 33:29.131
Just follow me.

33:30.121 --> 33:31.440
Congratulations, Old Madam Cui.

33:31.441 --> 33:33.200
Mr. Ji has ranked third place
in the palace examination,

33:33.201 --> 33:35.941
becoming the youngest first-class
metropolitan graduate.

33:36.791 --> 33:37.790
That's the first one.

33:37.791 --> 33:40.430
Secondly, Seventh Master Dou has learned

33:40.431 --> 33:43.751
of Old Madam Cui's generous efforts
in disaster relief.

33:43.751 --> 33:44.960
He has visited the local community

33:44.961 --> 33:48.181
and secured a commendation for you
from the imperial court.

33:48.551 --> 33:49.440
Usually,

33:49.441 --> 33:51.941
we all benefit greatly
from your support.

33:52.311 --> 33:54.920
We'll surely stop by
for the celebration tomorrow

33:54.921 --> 33:56.661
to share in the joy!

33:57.031 --> 33:57.940
All right.

33:57.941 --> 34:00.470
Well, we'll take our leave for now.

34:00.471 --> 34:01.851
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

34:01.851 --> 34:03.431
You don't have to see us off, Old Madam.

34:04.161 --> 34:05.761
- Come on out.
- Did you hear that?

34:05.991 --> 34:07.291
As a family,

34:07.311 --> 34:09.221
we should be open and honest.

34:10.591 --> 34:11.731
Let's go.

34:14.801 --> 34:15.941
- Grandmother.
- Grandmother.

34:18.631 --> 34:21.331
Did you all hear that just now?

34:22.471 --> 34:24.110
Originally,
Fourth Young Lady was worried

34:24.111 --> 34:26.411
about your relationship
with Seventh Master Dou.

34:26.671 --> 34:27.931
But it's all good now.

34:28.281 --> 34:29.550
As long as there's an intention,

34:29.551 --> 34:30.510
there's no grudge

34:30.511 --> 34:32.661
that cannot be mended
between a mother and a son.

34:32.801 --> 34:34.800
Father has shown
his sincerity this time.

34:34.801 --> 34:36.621
Grandmother should be pleased now.

34:37.281 --> 34:38.771
Small favors

34:38.921 --> 34:40.621
don't matter to me

34:41.991 --> 34:43.491
She may not admit it.

34:43.591 --> 34:46.470
But this morning,
she made shepherd's purse dumplings

34:46.471 --> 34:48.021
and sent them to Seventh Master Dou.

34:48.801 --> 34:50.760
Why can't you be more tight-lipped?

34:50.761 --> 34:52.621
Do you have to tell them everything?

34:53.281 --> 34:55.320
Ah, it's my fault. I'm sorry.

34:55.321 --> 34:56.630
But didn't Grandmother just say

34:56.631 --> 34:58.960
that we should be open
and honest as a family?

34:58.961 --> 34:59.920
That's right.

34:59.921 --> 35:01.590
I've never seen you this happy.

35:01.591 --> 35:02.771
Why don't you just admit it?

35:03.961 --> 35:05.360
You little rascals.

35:05.361 --> 35:07.811
Fine, I can't win against you.

35:10.401 --> 35:12.331
(Dou's Residence)
The teacher has been praising

35:12.551 --> 35:14.621
Ming's poetry lately.

35:14.631 --> 35:17.021
Shiying, why not test her a little?

35:17.241 --> 35:19.101
Ming learns the four arts

35:19.321 --> 35:22.261
for her own joy and relaxation.

35:22.551 --> 35:25.101
Testing her would only spoil the fun.

35:26.191 --> 35:27.331
You're right about that.

35:28.321 --> 35:29.461
My dear,

35:29.471 --> 35:30.741
how about taking a break

35:30.961 --> 35:32.541
and having some dessert?

35:34.071 --> 35:37.320
Mother sent shepherd's purse dumplings
this afternoon.

35:37.321 --> 35:38.741
I already had a few extra bowls.

35:38.921 --> 35:41.541
I really can't eat any more right now.

35:44.441 --> 35:45.581
Father,

35:45.801 --> 35:47.550
Mother knows you've been busy
with work lately

35:47.551 --> 35:48.691
and feeling a bit heated.

35:48.991 --> 35:51.720
She spent the whole afternoon making
this Golden Osmanthus Taro Milk.

35:51.721 --> 35:54.101
It's perfect for soothing
and boosting energy.

35:57.241 --> 35:58.451
Serve a bowl for me.

36:08.801 --> 36:09.971
A sweet treat

36:10.151 --> 36:12.491
after a hearty meal is perfect.

36:13.551 --> 36:16.070
So you like shepherd's purse dumplings.

36:16.071 --> 36:18.581
I'll make them more often for you
from now on.

36:20.111 --> 36:22.581
When I was little,
I often had indigestion.

36:23.191 --> 36:25.800
Mother would make
these dumplings for me.

36:25.801 --> 36:26.971
They always helped.

36:28.801 --> 36:31.261
After Mother moved to the manor,

36:31.761 --> 36:32.931
no one could make them

36:33.441 --> 36:34.811
the same way.

36:37.961 --> 36:39.240
In a few days,

36:39.241 --> 36:41.061
the commendation
for Mother will come through.

36:42.151 --> 36:43.701
It'll be the perfect time

36:43.921 --> 36:45.920
to ask her to come
with me to the capital

36:45.921 --> 36:47.361
so I can take care of her
and fulfill my duty as a son.

36:47.361 --> 36:48.621
What do you think?

36:50.281 --> 36:52.190
You've been running around tirelessly

36:52.191 --> 36:53.491
for this commendation.

36:53.991 --> 36:55.491
If you two can reconcile,

36:55.641 --> 36:57.371
it would be a blessing
for the whole family.

36:57.991 --> 37:00.261
To know you think that way
puts my mind at ease.

37:01.511 --> 37:04.210
Master, Provincial Administration Commissioner,
Official Lu is here.

37:04.431 --> 37:06.601
Please invite him to Tongwen Hall
and serve him some tea.

37:06.991 --> 37:08.131
Yes, Master.

37:14.321 --> 37:15.461
I'll excuse myself.

37:25.191 --> 37:26.331
Master.

37:26.631 --> 37:27.771
I'm fine.

37:28.361 --> 37:29.501
Mother,

37:29.591 --> 37:31.440
Father still cares about you.

37:31.441 --> 37:32.550
He was clearly full

37:32.551 --> 37:34.491
but he still drank
your Golden Osmanthus Taro Milk.

37:35.671 --> 37:37.491
He wasn't caring about me.

37:37.801 --> 37:39.741
He was clearly playing favorites.

37:40.671 --> 37:43.411
When that old woman
really brings Dou Zhao back here,

37:43.631 --> 37:46.411
do you think we can still speak up
in Dou's Residence?

37:46.621 --> 37:48.521
(Cui's Residence)

37:49.631 --> 37:52.451
Fifth Uncle took ten years
to pass the imperial exam.

37:52.671 --> 37:54.190
But Ji's different.

37:54.191 --> 37:55.491
He's young

37:55.511 --> 37:57.261
and he ranked third on his first try!

37:57.361 --> 37:59.960
If it were me, I'd throw a big banquet

37:59.961 --> 38:01.811
and show off to all the relatives.

38:01.991 --> 38:03.131
But him?

38:03.131 --> 38:04.601
He doesn't even bother to come back.

38:05.681 --> 38:08.101
He was never fond of celebrations.

38:08.321 --> 38:10.891
He will only think
that they're boring and a waste of time.

38:10.961 --> 38:13.261
Only you understand
his weird personality.

38:13.601 --> 38:15.800
Still, making it to the top ranks
is a good thing, right?

38:15.801 --> 38:17.030
But look at his letter.

38:17.031 --> 38:18.361
It's all complaints and frustration.

38:18.361 --> 38:20.470
The emperor asked him
about his ambitions in court.

38:20.471 --> 38:22.670
He said he aimed to become
the Grand Secretary within ten years

38:22.671 --> 38:24.360
and overhaul
the court's corrupt practices.

38:24.361 --> 38:25.771
Bold aspirations indeed.

38:25.841 --> 38:27.440
This isn't some theatrical play.

38:27.441 --> 38:28.590
His ambition is too much.

38:28.591 --> 38:31.360
The Emperor scolded him for being
too ambitious, chasing fame and power.

38:31.361 --> 38:32.621
Overhauling the court

38:32.621 --> 38:34.800
would make all the officials
in the court seem like a problem.

38:34.801 --> 38:35.941
Who would tolerate him?

38:37.671 --> 38:39.371
His Majesty didn't make him
the top scholar

38:39.511 --> 38:41.181
or let him join Hanlin Academy.

38:41.441 --> 38:43.371
Instead, he was sent
to oversee things in Futing.

38:43.671 --> 38:45.181
With Ji Yong's pride,

38:45.591 --> 38:46.731
he can't endure that long.

38:47.111 --> 38:48.040
Forget it.

38:48.041 --> 38:48.880
Someone like him cannot be brought

38:48.881 --> 38:50.851
into the Zhao Family
as a matrilocal husband.

38:50.851 --> 38:52.301
Or else I would never figure
him out in a lifetime.

38:53.191 --> 38:54.840
Aren't you eating?

38:54.841 --> 38:56.891
No. I want to reply to his letter first.

39:12.021 --> 39:19.321
(Revere Heaven and Ancestral Wisdom)

39:19.401 --> 39:20.541
Your Majesty,

39:20.961 --> 39:23.280
it was because Duke of Ding
misused his power

39:23.281 --> 39:24.470
and was indulgent

39:24.471 --> 39:26.670
that Futing became full
of corrupt officials,

39:26.671 --> 39:29.101
leading to flooding
and the suffering of the people.

39:29.111 --> 39:31.291
I urge everyone to submit a petition

39:31.551 --> 39:33.811
to impeach Duke of Ding tomorrow
for his abuse of power

39:33.841 --> 39:34.981
and indulgence.

39:37.681 --> 39:38.670
- Yes.
- Yes.

39:38.671 --> 39:40.511
Surely you haven't forgotten, right?

39:40.841 --> 39:43.411
(Liang Jifang, Minister of Revenue)
It was Duke of Ding's influence

39:43.671 --> 39:47.190
that Futing's sea trade remained smooth
for a decade without incident.

39:47.191 --> 39:47.730
(Wu Yifen)
Are you saying

39:47.731 --> 39:48.630
(Grand Secretary of Grand Secretariat)
Are you saying

39:48.631 --> 39:50.971
that it was Duke of Ding's work alone?

39:51.731 --> 39:52.590
Here.

39:52.591 --> 39:54.451
Your father
is the Minister of Personnel.

39:54.511 --> 39:56.030
(Gu Yu, Earl of Yunyang)
Just tell your father to scold Duke of Ding

39:56.031 --> 39:57.070
for being lazy and tyrannical
in governance.

39:57.071 --> 39:58.211
All right.

39:58.321 --> 40:00.491
Your father is the Vice Minister
of Revenue.

40:00.671 --> 40:02.291
Let him say Duke of Ding neglects

40:02.401 --> 40:03.400
his wife and family.

40:03.401 --> 40:04.800
Lazy and tyrannical.

40:04.801 --> 40:06.181
Neglects his wife and family.

40:06.591 --> 40:07.960
You've mixed them up.

40:07.961 --> 40:09.101
Your father...

40:10.671 --> 40:11.891
Wait, mixing them up works too.

40:11.961 --> 40:13.720
Duke of Ding's lazy
and tyrannical governance

40:13.721 --> 40:15.320
should be punished.

40:15.321 --> 40:17.550
He should be sent to a remote border

40:17.551 --> 40:19.520
to avoid causing further trouble.

40:19.521 --> 40:21.590
Duke of Ding commands the Ding Army.

40:21.591 --> 40:23.030
Yet, he neglects his wife and family

40:23.031 --> 40:24.110
and abuses others,

40:24.111 --> 40:25.470
(Zhu Siyuan, the Emperor)
resulting in no heir.

40:25.471 --> 40:27.621
That makes him unfilial as well.

40:27.671 --> 40:29.741
I must disagree with you, minister.

40:29.881 --> 40:32.661
It's a serious crime for the Ding Army
to embezzle military pay.

40:33.111 --> 40:35.141
I ask Your Majesty
to punish him severely

40:35.151 --> 40:36.771
to protect the nation.

40:37.511 --> 40:39.371
I delivered your words exactly
as you instructed.

40:39.761 --> 40:41.101
But I still don't understand.

40:41.511 --> 40:42.701
Putting aside the impeachment.

40:42.991 --> 40:44.541
The accusations from both sides

40:44.591 --> 40:45.630
contradict each other.

40:45.631 --> 40:46.771
That's the point.

40:46.971 --> 40:48.720
When His Majesty sees
them making up baseless

40:48.721 --> 40:49.670
and nonsensical charges,

40:49.671 --> 40:51.670
he'll realize Uncle is a loyal official

40:51.671 --> 40:52.811
with no faction.

40:52.991 --> 40:55.221
His suspicion and distrust
will naturally fade away.

40:59.801 --> 41:01.141
Contradicting each other.

41:02.991 --> 41:04.491
Utterly nonsense.

41:12.671 --> 41:13.811
Your Majesty.

41:21.221 --> 41:22.310
When you think about it...

41:22.311 --> 41:23.481
That's right.

41:29.471 --> 41:31.411
Official Wu. Official Wu.

41:35.111 --> 41:37.331
It wasn't intended for you.

41:37.671 --> 41:38.920
When the emperor asks,

41:38.921 --> 41:41.181
I can only speak honestly.

41:43.281 --> 41:44.851
Honestly, huh?

41:45.401 --> 41:47.240
As long as
it's for the court's stability,

41:47.241 --> 41:48.761
it's all well and good.

41:48.991 --> 41:51.701
But this concerns major matters
in the southeast.

41:52.281 --> 41:54.661
Doesn't it seem unrelated
to the Ministry of Rites?

41:57.511 --> 41:59.101
With the Dragon Boat Festival
approaching,

41:59.591 --> 42:04.971
why don't you go home
and rest for a few days?

42:08.401 --> 42:09.621
I shall comply

42:09.631 --> 42:11.541
with your command.

42:42.921 --> 42:44.240
Mr. Wu Shan is unconscious.

42:44.241 --> 42:46.400
Fourth Young Lady ordered someone
to carry him to the back yard.

42:46.401 --> 42:47.360
How dare you harm

42:47.361 --> 42:48.440
Official Wu's only grandson?

42:48.441 --> 42:49.440
Mr. Wu would be dead

42:49.441 --> 42:50.920
by the time the physician arrived.

42:50.921 --> 42:53.411
Dou Zhao, are you trying
to get the entire family killed?

42:53.411 --> 42:55.070
Since you're skilled
in reading facial expressions,

42:55.071 --> 42:56.581
you will know I'm not lying.

42:57.031 --> 42:58.170
I can save him.

42:58.171 --> 43:02.650
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:02.651 --> 43:06.411
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:06.571 --> 43:10.961
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:11.141 --> 43:15.070
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:15.071 --> 43:18.050
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:18.051 --> 43:20.260
♪Or perhaps my heart yearns
for the other side♪

43:20.261 --> 43:22.821
♪Yet there's no place for me to go
in the end♪

43:22.871 --> 43:26.441
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

43:26.501 --> 43:30.021
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

43:30.031 --> 43:34.010
♪That brings me through
a chapter of my life♪

43:34.011 --> 43:38.041
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

43:38.481 --> 43:41.941
♪Having you is a blessing♪

43:42.101 --> 43:44.281
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

43:44.301 --> 43:48.131
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

43:48.461 --> 43:51.601
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

43:52.141 --> 43:55.551
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

43:55.991 --> 43:59.531
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

43:59.731 --> 44:03.400
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:03.401 --> 44:07.741
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:07.801 --> 44:11.530
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:11.531 --> 44:15.010
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:15.011 --> 44:19.691
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:19.721 --> 44:23.310
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

44:23.311 --> 44:27.451
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

44:27.521 --> 44:30.811
♪Always together, looking back♪

44:31.121 --> 44:38.421
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

44:47.741 --> 44:48.700
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:48.701 --> 44:49.740
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:49.741 --> 44:50.961
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
